{"tid":2342825,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"救人一命 - 杜杜","createTime":"2020-12-27T12:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T12:15:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9be45f3e34d8cb944ba4939c65394d678e98f9f","tid":2342825,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201226/BZLFJ6FK45HP5F2RFSVR2XRYFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201226%2FBZLFJ6FK45HP5F2RFSVR2XRYFI%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWCQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=0f68da39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201226%2FBZLFJ6FK45HP5F2RFSVR2XRYFI%2F&h=12833ebb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201226/BZLFJ6FK45HP5F2RFSVR2XRYFI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n救人一命 - 杜杜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AoqxpG0msFK7SvjBlV19lJ9Au94=/780x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MLYZFZZS3JH5FJH324OZCRL5UA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAoqxpG0msFK7SvjBlV19lJ9Au94%3D%2F780x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMLYZFZZS3JH5FJH324OZCRL5UA.jpg&h=5189e9c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Viridiana》劇照<br />\n<br />\n超現實大師布紐爾的電影&ldquo;Viridiana&rdquo;裏面有這樣的一幕：有人在路上趕馬車，馬車底下縛着一隻狗，在車輪之間以急速的步伐跟着馬車的速度前進。善心人士看不過眼，出錢買了那隻狗，把牠從困境中解救出來。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過電影中的這一幕一直在我腦海中浮現，揮之不去。救了一隻狗，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n這個世界，甚至於這個宇宙，也只不過是通過了人的意識才能夠呈現，才會產生意義。這個人的意識，也就是這個「我」。世界上有千千萬萬的「我」，但是所有的「我」在本質上是同一樣東西。托爾斯泰在晚年的日記中就記下了這一感悟。弄明白了這一點，也就完全明白：「救了一個人，也就是救了一整個世界。」<br />\n<br />\n傳聞斯太林說過這樣的話（也有人說其實是一位德國作家說的）：。。。。。。。。。。"}]}